snippet.title: Ex Astris Official Launch PV「Ordorbis」EN Ver.
snippet.description:
From thousands of light years away, we're setting sails into the stars.
All you need is to believe 
that the twinkling stars will light your path and the fate of yours shall guide you through.

Ex Astris Coming soon on Feb 27 (0:00 UTC+8). 
Pre-order now: https://exa.gryphline.com/en-us
